MANOSABA-MIND_SHARD.description:
Choose 1 of 3 random Attack cards from another witch to add to your hand. It costs 0 this turn.
{IfUpgraded:show:
Upgrade the chosen card.}

MANOSABA-STARBURST_STREAM.description:
Exhaust your hand.
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage {Repeat} times. Each hit deals +1 damage per card Exhausted.{IfUpgraded:show:
At the end, deal 30% of the total damage again (Unpowered).}

MANOSABA-HIRO_PUPPET.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage.
Add a copy of this card to your [gold]Discard pile[/gold].{IfUpgraded:show:
If you have played [gold]Ema Puppet[/gold] this combat, heal HP equal to 20% of damage dealt.|}

MANOSABA-MIRIA_PUPPET.description:
[gold]Transform[/gold] up to {Cards:diff()} card(s) in your [gold]Hand[/gold].
Attack, Skill, and Power cards always become cards whose names contain "Puppet".{IfUpgraded:show:
Upgrade the transformed cards.|}

MANOSABA-EMERGENCY_SUTURE.description:
[gold]Exhaust[/gold] all of your [gold]Status[/gold] cards.
For each card [gold]Exhausted[/gold] this way, deal {Damage:diff()} damage to ALL enemies.{InCombat:
(Hits {CalculatedHits:diff()} {CalculatedHits:plural:time|times})|}
